Scope: Restore the two missing npm scripts to the complete three-script set mandated by the structure: `"dev": "tsx src/main.ts"`, `"start": "tsx src/main.ts"`, and `"typecheck": "tsc --noEmit"`. Add `@anthropic-ai/sdk` at `^0.104.1` to `dependencies` and run `npm install`. Verify that `npm run typecheck` passes with zero errors and the system remains runnable (existing passthrough still responds correctly to `curl POST /v1/chat/completions`). This is a MODIFY-only task fixing the single-file regression identified by the backward loop, incorporating the lesson that all three scripts must be explicitly preserved.
